		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alex Sze]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2020 10:51:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[科技小tips]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://34.83.168.187/?p=591</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[MACBOOK 擁有手提電腦界其中一款最好用嘅TRACKPAD，但係FFRabbit 身邊就好小有真正識用MACBOOK TRACKPAD嘅人。所以今日就等FFRabbit 為大家介紹一下MACBOOK TRACKPAD 有用又好玩嘅三項功能啦！ 首先，打開SYSTEM PREFERENCE，然後按TRACKPAD 先確認一下你嘅MACBOOK 有冇以下嘅功能：Look up &#38; data detectors, Smart zoom, Swipe between pages。（如果冇顯示可能係你嘅MACBOOK 暫時唔支援呢啲功能。）然後點選方格開啟功能。 Look up &#38; data detectors 呢項功能係FFRabbit 覺得最有用嘅MACBOOK 功能之一。呢個功能減省左搜尋資料嘅步驟，令你可以更快取得心水資料。想使用呢項功能嘅你，只需要選取希望查閱嘅字，然後Force Click （亦即係大力小小㩒個TRACKPAD），螢幕上就會顯示翻譯及詳細資料。識用呢項功能之後，你就唔再需要GOOGLE Search 啦！ Smart zoom 相信唔小貪方便嘅朋友都同FFRabbit 一樣選擇左13吋嘅MACBOOK，然後經常因為螢幕太細而睇唔清楚螢幕內容。Smart zoom就正正係為咗解決呢個問題而出現。想使用呢項功能嘅你，只需要將鼠標移到希望放大嘅位置，然後雙指Double Click，就可以暫時放大該區域。而想還原嘅時侯，就可以重覆雙指Double Click動作。相信呢項功能可以解決唔小人嘅煩惱。 Swipe between pages 呢項功能取代左瀏覽器左上角位置嘅&#8221;回到前/後一頁&#8221;，令瀏覽網頁更方便快捷。想使用呢項功能嘅你，只需要雙指往右（回到前一頁）或雙指往左（回到後一頁）移動就可以完成前進/返回操作。呢項功能係FFRabbit 其中一項最常使用嘅功能之一。 最後，希望以上小教學可以幫助到大家提升工作效率啦！]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>MACBOOK 擁有手提電腦界其中一款最好用嘅TRACKPAD，但係FFRabbit 身邊就好小有真正識用MACBOOK TRACKPAD嘅人。所以今日就等FFRabbit 為大家介紹一下MACBOOK TRACKPAD 有用又好玩嘅三項功能啦！</p>



<p>首先，打開SYSTEM PREFERENCE，然後按TRACKPAD 先確認一下你嘅MACBOOK 有冇以下嘅功能：Look up &amp; data detectors, Smart zoom, Swipe between pages。（如果冇顯示可能係你嘅MACBOOK 暫時唔支援呢啲功能。）然後點選方格開啟功能。</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="396" height="405" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.43.06.png" alt="" class="wp-image-594" srcset="https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.43.06.png 396w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.43.06-293x300.png 293w" sizes="(max-width: 396px) 100vw, 396px" /></figure></div>



<p style="font-size:30px;font-weight:bold" class="has-custom-weight"><strong>Look up &amp; data detectors</strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="823" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.43-1024x823.png" alt="" class="wp-image-595" srcset="https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.43-1024x823.png 1024w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.43-300x241.png 300w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.43-768x617.png 768w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.43-1536x1235.png 1536w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.43.png 1560w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>呢項功能係FFRabbit 覺得最有用嘅MACBOOK 功能之一。呢個功能減省左搜尋資料嘅步驟，令你可以更快取得心水資料。想使用呢項功能嘅你，只需要選取希望查閱嘅字，然後Force Click （亦即係大力小小㩒個TRACKPAD），螢幕上就會顯示翻譯及詳細資料。識用呢項功能之後，你就唔再需要GOOGLE Search 啦！</p>



<p style="font-size:30px"><strong>Smart zoom</strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="823" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.48-1024x823.png" alt="" class="wp-image-596" srcset="https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.48-1024x823.png 1024w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.48-300x241.png 300w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.48-768x617.png 768w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.48-1536x1235.png 1536w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.48.png 1560w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>相信唔小貪方便嘅朋友都同FFRabbit 一樣選擇左13吋嘅MACBOOK，然後經常因為螢幕太細而睇唔清楚螢幕內容。Smart zoom就正正係為咗解決呢個問題而出現。想使用呢項功能嘅你，只需要將鼠標移到希望放大嘅位置，然後雙指Double Click，就可以暫時放大該區域。而想還原嘅時侯，就可以重覆雙指Double Click動作。相信呢項功能可以解決唔小人嘅煩惱。</p>



<p style="font-size:30px"><strong>Swipe between pages</strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="823" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.55-1024x823.png" alt="" class="wp-image-597" srcset="https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.55-1024x823.png 1024w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.55-300x241.png 300w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.55-768x617.png 768w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.55-1536x1235.png 1536w, https://https://alexsze.github.io/ffrabbit/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screenshot-2020-07-14-at-18.42.55.png 1560w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>呢項功能取代左瀏覽器左上角位置嘅&#8221;回到前/後一頁&#8221;，令瀏覽網頁更方便快捷。想使用呢項功能嘅你，只需要雙指往右（回到前一頁）或雙指往左（回到後一頁）移動就可以完成前進/返回操作。呢項功能係FFRabbit 其中一項最常使用嘅功能之一。</p>



<p>最後，希望以上小教學可以幫助到大家提升工作效率啦！</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
